title: Café of the Seven Sinners 1940 (directed by Tay Garnett) Marlene Dietrich & John Wayne

sources.title: Café of the Seven Sinners 1940 (directed by Tay Garnett) Marlene Dietrich & John Wayne
sources.description:
HE'S FIGHTING-MAD! Battling and brawling for her lips!
A torch singer (Marlene Dietrich) wows a Navy officer (John Wayne) and his shipmates at a South Seas cafe.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/ULm3VX5BDWw


Original title: Seven Sinners (1940)
Alternative titles: Cafe of the Seven Sinners, La maison des 7 péchés, Siete pecadores, De isla en isla, Das Haus der sieben Sünden, La taverna dei sette peccati, Sju syndare, Bizsu, A Pecadora, Οι Επτά Αμαρτωλοί, Семь грешников, 七枭雄, 세븐 시너스, Șapte păcate, Seitsemän syntistä, Siedmiu grzeszników

Director: Tay Garnett
Writers: John Meehan, Harry Tugend, Ladislas Fodor
Stars: Marlene Dietrich, John Wayne, Albert Dekker
Genres: Comedy, Drama, Romance
